title: Bandit Burrito
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Take-out, Mexican, Catering, Tex-Mex, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. The chef will create custom burritos, salads, tortilla bowls, and nachos for you, built the way you like with fresh ingredients made in-house daily. Veggie toppings include vegetarian chorizo sausage, guacamole, choice of fresh salasa, beans, white or wild rice, seasonal fajita vegetables. Casual, family atmosphere.
